{"tid":1965590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國民黨: 台灣防疫展現高水準, WHO應平等對待台灣","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T15:37:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed88937c8464f21e1d9bf2b9055c0915f390e23","tid":1965590,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"早前, 國民黨仲鼓吹捐口罩俾大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家終於甦醒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-09/388708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-09%2F388708&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=8903f38c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-09/388708</a><br />\n<br />\n昔日鼓吹捐口罩 國民黨今籲譚德塞 WHO應拋開「大國」政治羈絆<br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 黃建豪 台北市報導<br />\n發布 2020.04.09 | 13:56<br />\n<br />\n就世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞指控，遭受來自台灣的人身攻擊。國民黨中央今（9日）也發出聲明表達立場，稱「不樂見在我國參與世衛組織討論中，任何泛政治化的攻訐或挑釁式的言語」，WHO應平等對待我國，支持我國重返WHO。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨下午發表聲明稱，中華民國是國際醫療體系的一員，長期致力於醫療服務以及國際公益。國民黨執政時期參與世衛大會及專家會議時，也成功地貢獻所能，得到世界多國的認同。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨表示，面對本次新冠肺炎疫情，我國不僅展現高水準的公衛防疫能力，更顯示我國不應該因為任何理由而被排除於世衛組織之外。國民黨主張，WHO應拋開大國政治的羈絆，遵守該組織憲章，嚴肅並平等地對待我國以及2350萬同胞。國民黨無論執政或在野，均全力支持可讓我國重返世衛組織之理性、靈活外交政策。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨表示，國民黨不樂見在我國參與世衛組織討論中，任何泛政治化的攻訐或挑釁式的言語，因為這些無助於我國的參與，國民黨相信我國國民多能理性討論，念茲在茲的都是讓我國於今年5月順利參與世衛大會，貢獻己力。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨稱，WHO主管不應在未有明確證據的情況下，便將其近來所受之抨擊均歸咎於台灣，且不應漠視長期以來我國願有意義參與世衛大會的強烈訴求，因為兩者已明顯損害國人的國際形象與健康權。"},{"pid":"eda5fb21449d4881e94d9d9d6e64d304ede7d5e4","tid":1965590,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1198b16e0ad4822e713bea7381ba4e1ba57ef31","tid":1965590,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82e8ffc7eaabcd597e1ce519f1b5e4f3e3cab54","tid":1965590,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df3880330af54ef5b8a660b1fcf8793b855cbf6","tid":1965590,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e6af8499ba38d30425a0844f6c44fb647f2a92","tid":1965590,"uid":6132,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"平等對待台灣=同其他國家相同待遇=比台灣做成員國=承認台灣為主權國家=國民黨台獨<br />\n來人，把这台独给我B了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c897cdf100d98d5ed8790a157558c6a6f2f360da","tid":1965590,"uid":32371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"扮下野姐"},{"pid":"c4a8abef285430ec2cba2ac2fdb984a287045dbb","tid":1965590,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"甦醒? no, 跟大勢"},{"pid":"38b462afeb5f39de77862d41130cc79b9e3728d9","tid":1965590,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4a8abef285430ec2cba2ac2fdb984a287045dbb","tid":1965590,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"甦醒? no, 跟大勢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"似係...."},{"pid":"f61b1610ceec3add9896ceff7cf07638af77b178","tid":1965590,"uid":305080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"搶光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38529fd18d0918dbe41cb2111fa41a1c92bf5497","tid":1965590,"uid":103981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"国民党企開D啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"9f1b2d5274e1afaa3d9